{"tid":1973861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同意學生父親到家幫按摩 女補教師引狼入室遭性侵","createTime":"2020-04-15T12:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T23:49:26.000Z","uid":84102,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5a1ed5336f6554ebaaf3fd43c92c0e353542451d","tid":1973861,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/04/15/phpjWKWC4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F04%2F15%2FphpjWKWC4.jpg&h=96e3e72c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（情境照）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔記者王俊忠／台南報導〕單親、育有女兒的蔡姓男健身教練，因女兒上補習班緣故，與教女兒的女補教師常有聯繫，一回深夜，女教師因睡不著，蔡男自告奮勇稱可為女師按摩、放鬆肌肉，女師竟同意蔡男暗夜到她家幫做按摩，按摩過程長達2、3小時，引發蔡男性慾、趁機以手指侵入女師下體，女師反抗稱有男友快結婚，仍無法抵擋男方攻勢。台南高分院依強制性侵罪判蔡男3年2月徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n判決指出，2017年11月25日凌晨1、2點時，女教師同意蔡男到她位於台南市的住處1樓，讓蔡男在1樓客廳為女師做按摩，一直到凌晨4、5點按摩結束，蔡居然按到性慾高漲，突然撲向女方、壓在沙發上，不顧女師反抗推拒、表明拒絕，強行用手指從女師短褲縫裡伸入下體「指侵」，對女方強制性侵得逞。"},{"pid":"7cc53edf14ad124ba5bb4c013d00c7130fdd4810","tid":1973861,"uid":231583,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:50:09.000Z","msg":"女師竟同意蔡男暗夜到她家幫做按摩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e269e3fc9ca8895ac7f3bcc8a5328f9317e9a2d","tid":1973861,"uid":88374,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:50:30.000Z","msg":"條女都有問題啦"},{"pid":"3182c1247b5611b823872a8832ff259ad7dd3d99","tid":1973861,"uid":157411,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:50:47.000Z","msg":"勞資糾紛"},{"pid":"0d47adf923f52fe205723c3523eb55dda7973c79","tid":1973861,"uid":245065,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67bcb455ddcf3e686ce7d69ef4be48a37be7097f","tid":1973861,"uid":230594,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:53:20.000Z","msg":"連登慣性首先Blame the victim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0baaffbd357db5d0a1cc0894548734edef8b6f","tid":1973861,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:53:26.000Z","msg":"第一桶金"},{"pid":"a84a923c4ce02d8aba832b29303e55a17ab7828d","tid":1973861,"uid":164497,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:55:31.000Z","msg":"太急啦, 按慣左, 抽開水終會有一次忍唔住想搞"},{"pid":"097013e0539d6caa7251aae791ad4566012a63cf","tid":1973861,"uid":164497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a84a923c4ce02d8aba832b29303e55a17ab7828d","tid":1973861,"uid":164497,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:55:31.000Z","msg":"太急啦, 按慣左, 抽開水終會有一次忍唔住想搞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:55:58.000Z","msg":"另外忘了不推文回覆"},{"pid":"3f8167a90e7e122ec8e068a4160fd35ce1a5db57","tid":1973861,"uid":7699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:56:24.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係新北"},{"pid":"003be853f75e67e94fb331c511c501b4b83d9dfa","tid":1973861,"uid":28068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e269e3fc9ca8895ac7f3bcc8a5328f9317e9a2d","tid":1973861,"uid":88374,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:50:30.000Z","msg":"條女都有問題啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:56:47.000Z","msg":"無錢收咪提告"},{"pid":"ac657abb7d471e183982cb86ea67a3ae1313477a","tid":1973861,"uid":161374,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"睇標題就知係台灣"},{"pid":"b3459480473bb91e42df0a4676917445b6df75cf","tid":1973861,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a84a923c4ce02d8aba832b29303e55a17ab7828d","tid":1973861,"uid":164497,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:55:31.000Z","msg":"太急啦, 按慣左, 抽開水終會有一次忍唔住想搞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:57:08.000Z","msg":"關咩事<br />\n無錢ja"},{"pid":"8d48c7efd9fbd035003afc41739c108b33fcfd8b","tid":1973861,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:58:03